  "keyFeatures": [
    "Manage Zoom Phone sites with emergency addresses and short extension ranges",
    "Configure call queues with members, phone numbers, and voicemail policies",
    "Set up auto receptionists with IVR (Interactive Voice Response) systems",
    "Control call handling for business hours, closed hours, and holiday hours",
    "Manage shared line groups for shared phone number and extension access",
    "Assign calling plans and phone numbers to Zoom Phone users",
    "Manage blocked call lists and external contacts",
    "OAuth-based authentication using Server-to-Server app credentials",
    "Full import support for all resources using Terraform import"
